race.comment: The babies kick us off. LADY OF FIVE (4) has looked dominant winning both trials in easy fashion and rider Thompson stays on board for race day. Only needs some luck navigating from the outside alley to be featuring in the finish. COURTHEZON (1) saluted in a recent Warwick Farm trial and is sure to be well-educated out of the Archibald camp. Respect any push in betting. DREAM ROCA (3) won a recent Sunny Coast trial by over six lengths and could start the career on a positive note. RAROTONGA (2) showed ability in a recent trial victory and any market confidence must be heeded. The well-related RUN LIKE A GIRL (6) (half to Listed winner Bona Sforza) best of the rest in an interesting affair.
